Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.40,0:15:32.96,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,視野が狭く　今と己のことしか考えない
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.96,0:15:34.49,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,反省も　展望もない
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.94,0:15:36.22,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,ん　どうした
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.22,0:15:39.12,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,何でも　な　いや　あるかも
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.12,0:15:40.86,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,どうしよう　デパート行く
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.86,0:15:41.74,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,行く行く
