Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.98,0:16:08.20,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんが会いたくなくても会わせる
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.20,0:16:08.85,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,えっ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.65,0:16:10.56,JP-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,えっ
