Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.35,0:17:40.29,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,ボタンか
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.29,0:17:41.38,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,なんだと
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.38,0:17:43.66,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,デパートに怪しい一団が現れただと
