Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.20,0:00:06.10,ZH-Main-Down,Owl Woman,0,0,0,,最近雨多起來真苦惱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:08.08,ZH-Main-Down,Owl Man,0,0,0,,下雨難道不挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.08,0:00:11.24,ZH-Main-Down,Owl Man,0,0,0,,我們那最近天天下鯖魚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:14.79,ZH-Main-Down,Owl Man,0,0,0,,燒烤還是水煮都已經吃膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.79,0:00:18.74,ZH-Main-Down,Owl Woman,0,0,0,,青魚挺好 喜歡不喜歡都不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:26.35,ZH-Main-Down,Owl Woman,0,0,0,,列車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.89,0:00:28.77,ZH-Main-Down,Owl Man,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:32.36,ZH-Main-Down,Owl Man,0,0,0,,現在運行的只有池袋巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.40,0:00:44.80,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好快好快好快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:46.28,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留你冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:49.75,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,去吧去吧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:52.51,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,合葉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.51,0:00:55.03,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,池袋站是終端式站台
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:00:57.56,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸什麼 終端式站台是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.86,0:01:06.65,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這裡就是池袋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.92,0:01:08.78,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,差點以為要死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.78,0:01:09.67,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:10.99,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,有受傷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.99,0:01:12.13,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,但是太棒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.13,0:01:14.49,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,終於到達池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.49,0:01:16.97,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,說起來終端式站台
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:18.64,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,簡而言之就是死胡同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.43,0:01:21.88,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,怎麼了 波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:24.90,ZH-Main-Down,Leader,0,0,0,,發現入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:25.79,ZH-Main-Down,Leader,0,0,0,,快速排除
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.79,0:01:27.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 為什麼這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.37,0:01:28.90,ZH-Main-Down,Leader,0,0,0,,攻擊 上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.90,0:01:30.81,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真的沒用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.15,0:01:36.93,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香的氣味嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:37.41,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:38.45,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:40.03,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,等等我
Comment: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.75,ZH-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:14.55,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,您睡醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:16.95,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,飯菜已經為您準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:22.69,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:26.64,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,今天的飯菜 是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.91,0:03:29.93,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,魚乾還有蘑菇蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:31.59,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,加上苦瓜味噌湯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:33.36,ZH-Main-up-8,Yoka,0,0,0,,聽起來好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:36.68,ZH-Main-up-8,Yoka,0,0,0,,之前吃的也是苦瓜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:38.47,ZH-Main-up-8,Yoka,0,0,0,,你喜歡苦瓜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:41.27,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,不 並不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:43.02,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,是葉香大人您討厭它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:44.82,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,如果這樣 今後就
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:46.39,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.39,0:03:48.88,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,只是有些奇妙的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:51.12,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,奇妙的感覺是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:53.63,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,這我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:55.54,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,明明從未吃過它
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:57.58,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,但卻一股懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:03:59.13,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,所以才奇妙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:00.04,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:03.82,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,這個是 哪裡產的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:05.22,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,這個是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:09.02,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:14.84,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:16.69,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,去問問那個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:18.20,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:19.69,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我想問一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:23.53,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我們正在找一個叫中富葉香的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:27.88,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哇 好大塊頭的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:28.83,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,圍裙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:30.10,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,注意禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:34.66,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 怎麼怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:37.16,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:39.60,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,還是 混太郎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:45.85,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.11,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,挺可愛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:11.48,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,是你的狗狗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.48,0:05:13.46,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我曾經也養過一隻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:14.92,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,是叫波奇的狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:17.20,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,你 叫什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:20.86,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不是 它就是波奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:22.40,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,為什麼不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:25.93,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,大家都是從吾野來 接葉香你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:27.55,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你是葉香 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:41.32,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,你們 是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:44.44,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,難道你還在生我的氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:48.45,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:51.21,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我為什麼要生氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:52.29,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:11.77,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,總感覺 是非常的難受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:15.16,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,胸口 像火一樣灼燒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:16.40,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,等一下葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:18.40,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你難道不記得我們了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:20.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不是吧 失憶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:23.54,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,難道和善治郎一樣 被做了軟綿綿手術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:24.57,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:30.62,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我是中富葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.33,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,是一名喜歡天文學的高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.75,0:06:36.62,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,在池袋每天都認真學習
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:38.44,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,學習很快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:40.79,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,知曉未知也很快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:42.57,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,世界會膨脹的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:44.62,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,然後 將來的夢想是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:49.09,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,將來的 夢想是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:50.34,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:54.35,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:56.94,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:01.72,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,葉香大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:03.10,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,請您冷靜下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:05.15,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我是中富葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:06.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,聽我說葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:07.14,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:09.48,ZH-Main-Down,Vigilante,0,0,0,,她們還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:13.55,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,沒想到這麼快就找到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:16.41,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,傷害公主的臭蟲們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:18.57,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我們和與葉香公主同席
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:20.79,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,竟有如此老鼠屎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:22.13,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,總而言之是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:23.05,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,給我辦了她們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:25.44,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,總之 打倒她們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:26.84,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,看 這真的會死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.08,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,感覺要死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:28.93,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:30.46,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,等 葉香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.46,0:07:31.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留現在還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:32.91,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,大家來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:34.99,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,小命沒了前功盡棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:39.10,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,公主 您有受傷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:39.80,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:47.54,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼重要的東西會放在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:48.39,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你個鳥頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.39,0:07:50.06,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:51.20,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是那群傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.07,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.89,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,都是因為她們公主才
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:55.69,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,給我逮捕她們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:57.79,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,絕對別放跑她們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:07:59.91,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:01.36,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:03.74,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,快點快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:09.54,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,為什麼讓她們逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:13.42,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我要把你們都告訴公主 全都變成涼粉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.74,0:08:15.60,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,不好了糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:17.60,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,考慮到按鈕和公主的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:19.51,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是時候要好好考慮這兩件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:21.22,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,明明我是非常警惕的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:23.01,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,結果太天真了你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:28.36,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,有何吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:30.69,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你說有什麼吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:31.98,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你個大塊頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:34.29,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,趕快把公主搬到其它地方去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:34.83,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,為何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:36.93,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你放跑的那群人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:38.86,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,很有可能是來搶奪公主的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:40.59,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,這點事情都不能理解嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:43.88,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,但是她本人很有可能並不願意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:46.47,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,她很喜歡那個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:48.67,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,這個那個的理由怎麼那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:51.81,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你不是說公主就由你來守護嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:52.81,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.81,0:08:56.71,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,哪怕傷到脖子上的一根毛 也得給我好好記住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:08:57.46,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.46,0:08:58.63,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,準備轉向架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.63,0:09:00.01,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,警備人員也要增加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:05.60,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那個難道不是真葉香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:06.45,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:07.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,畢竟挺奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:09.86,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那麼奇怪的葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,竟然連我們都不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:15.20,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,怪確實挺奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:17.45,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我想她確實是葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:19.95,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:22.75,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,畢竟葉香也提到了波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:24.50,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,絕對是葉香本人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:27.70,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,也就是說 葉香的態度很氣憤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:28.95,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,絕交水平
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:30.16,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,絕交
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:31.81,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:34.81,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我要是葉香 也會和自己絕交
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:37.85,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:41.38,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這個是摩爾斯 摩斯密碼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:43.14,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,善治郎和誠老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:45.85,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,為什麼要通過苦瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:49.01,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,很有可能根系藤蔓的延伸 與吾野建立起了聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.32,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:52.55,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,從吾野到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:55.20,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,苦瓜最強了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.56,0:09:57.89,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,所以說誠老師她講了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:09:59.89,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,將苦瓜切開 截面為圓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:00.43,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:01.94,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留 菜刀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:06.12,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,測試測試
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:08.13,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:10.64,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,苦瓜裡傳來誠老師的聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:12.70,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,那作為日語來說確實挺可疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:17.05,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,好吵啊 我這能聽到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:18.66,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,是誠老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.96,0:10:21.87,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,噢 能看見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:24.07,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,看不見 聲音專用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:25.01,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:27.67,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我們已經找到了讓世界恢復原狀的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:28.90,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:30.38,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是善治郎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:31.66,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:35.66,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,雖然沒有得到證實 但是假說信服度落在置信區間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:39.95,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,7G開通的起點應該有作為開關的按鈕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:42.84,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,而那個按鈕 應該是開啟狀態的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:45.66,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,也就是說 再按一次按鈕的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:46.37,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:48.65,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,7G線路會被切斷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:51.34,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,電波的影響就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:53.93,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,也就是說很有可能回到原來的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:55.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,就這
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:56.90,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不是不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:58.16,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這太簡單了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:10:59.87,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,但這卻讓我們忽略了它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:03.09,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,我們太聚焦於應對個別現象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:06.16,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,根本沒有時間去探求「根本原因」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:07.79,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,這點確實
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:09.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,那個按鈕現在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:11.11,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,這點我們也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.11,0:11:13.90,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,但至少 假如我是龐太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:16.61,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,肯定會採取嚴密的警備措施
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:19.09,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,那些想要維持現狀的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:21.84,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,還有想回到過去狀態之人之間的爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:24.50,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,按鈕的存在將決定各自命運
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:27.84,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,如果有了新消息就再聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:30.88,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,通話過後的苦瓜可是非常好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:31.99,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:34.50,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,糟蹋糧食可不 吧吧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.07,0:11:37.38,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊嘞 變成平常的善治郎了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:42.85,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,雖然最近的哈吧吧模式的時間已經延長到五分三十八秒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:44.12,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這挺厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:47.15,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,不 距離完全的程度還很遠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:49.71,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這樣延長下去就能恢復原狀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:52.28,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,計算上需要九十四年以後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:55.02,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:56.98,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,稍微考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:12:00.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,九十四年以後善治郎都去世了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:01.76,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:03.19,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是按鈕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.19,0:12:07.47,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,也就是說 存在類似「核足球」的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:08.74,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:11.87,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,總統發射核武器的必要工具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:13.82,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,一般由警備人員時刻提攜著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:15.19,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這沒危險嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:17.02,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,要是被偷盜了該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:19.93,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,雖然這種情節小說和漫畫多得讓人髮指
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:21.70,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,現實卻並未發生過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.70,0:12:22.31,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:24.42,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香變得如此冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:26.32,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,有沒有可能是按鈕的問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.32,0:12:27.31,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:29.90,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,既然按下按鈕世界就會被改變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:31.81,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,再按一次就能關掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:33.98,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,世界和葉香都有可能恢復原狀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.37,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 確實
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:37.69,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,所以才有那種不好的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:38.76,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,等會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:39.84,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,就這
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:42.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,畢竟想到的只有這種可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:43.16,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,鼠目寸光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:44.35,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,人是會變的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:45.52,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,但是有一決勝負的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:46.89,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,先找到按鈕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:50.70,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,如果真有決勝機會 一定要做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:52.69,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好想法 贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:53.44,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:55.63,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,又是小晶你的但但是是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:56.51,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:58.00,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,找按鈕沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:12:59.92,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,雖然挺好但要怎麼找
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:01.59,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,找到它和得到它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:03.08,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是兩個任務啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:09.73,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:11.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,僵屍的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:14.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,是黑金
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:16.65,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.18,0:13:18.66,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:23.48,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,從那之後附近車站的環境變化挺大的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:26.96,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,要繼續這樣僵屍全體 要麼被黴菌腐蝕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:29.06,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,要麼被乾燥得成粉末了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:31.75,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,僵屍竟然如此敏感啊 好意外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:34.00,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以你要和我們合作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:36.78,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我們有數量優勢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:39.51,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,你們頭腦 有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.51,0:13:40.62,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,為什麼是疑問句
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:43.60,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,剛剛頭腦擔當誠老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:45.59,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,告訴我們 要是找到了終止7G的按鈕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:47.77,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,說不定就能有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:49.57,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,頭腦擔當是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.57,0:13:51.44,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你是肌肉擔當吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:53.28,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,那個按鈕在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:54.36,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:56.52,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是能把世界變成這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:57.81,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,必然擁有很強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:13:59.52,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,也就是說會很大的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:01.74,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 就好比酒桶那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.74,0:14:03.09,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,酒桶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:03.94,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:04.68,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.68,0:14:07.22,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,剛剛路過百貨商店的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:11.98,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,欸 怎麼了 發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:22.62,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,僵屍竟然對大腦和花菜以外的東西感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:25.50,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,說明僵屍們也想變回人類
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:28.45,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,這些僵屍們 很有可能是被「恢復」的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:31.46,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,也就是對擁有力量的按鈕 產生了反應
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:34.65,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,而那是按鈕的可能性就非常之高
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:36.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸 不是也可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:38.44,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那個商城啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:39.83,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我沒去過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:40.49,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:42.21,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,咱想過精緻的生活嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:43.88,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,而且咱最喜歡自己啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:46.73,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,之前看到類似的廣告就很嚮往
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:47.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,要去那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:49.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,可是 難得來到了池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:51.35,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,順便去看看也問題不大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:53.37,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你就只是想去商城罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:54.63,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,就是想購物罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:56.27,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,大家都想去商城
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:57.82,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,當然也要找按鈕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:14:58.49,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,虛偽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.49,0:15:01.15,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,龐太郎那群人肯定會把它隱藏起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:02.82,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,而且感覺他好像挺威風凌凌的
